description: Dan's US History Facts lets you ask Alexa for random facts about United States history. Just tell her to launch Dan's History Facts and ask for a fact and she'll tell you one of over seventy facts about United States history!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, start dan's history facts and tell me a history fact
Alexa, open dan's history facts and tell me another fact
name: Dan's US History Facts
shortDescription: Dan's US History Facts lets you ask Alexa for random facts about U.S. history.
